==English==

===Etymology===
"Jerk off" is vulgar slang meaning to masturbate. This is a variation on jerk.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|s}}
<!-- Is this American only? -->
# {{cattag|vulgar slang}} Someone who is rude or idiotic, especially a man.
#* ''He is a '''jerk-off'''. He had no reason to tell me to go kill myself.''